quran[11]{c,v,t}:
  43,46,"And We have certainly sent Moses with Our signs to Pharaoh and his assembly, then he said: I am a messenger from the Master of Human kind"
  43,47,"But when he brought them Our miracles, they laughed at it"
  43,48,And We did not show them any miracle unless it was bigger than its sister (the one before it). And We took them with the punishment so that they may return
  43,49,"And they said: magician, call on your Master for us according to His agreement with you, as we are indeed guided"
  43,50,"But when We removed the punishment from them, they immediately broke (their promise)"
  43,51,"And Pharaoh called out among his people, saying: my people, does not the rule of Egypt belong to me as do these rivers flowing underneath me? Do you not see"
  43,52,Am I not better than this one who is despicable and cannot express (himself) clearly
  43,53,So why bracelets of gold were not given to him or the angels did not come accompanying him
  43,54,Then he belittled his people and they obeyed him. Indeed they were disobedient people
  43,55,"So when they enraged Us, We took revenge from them and drowned them all"
  43,56,So We made them a thing of the past and an example for the later ones